293
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,519
Going out to eat this late.

294
00:13:47,399 --> 00:13:49,639
I was working late. Didn't have time to eat.

295
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:50,960
I'm hungry now.

296
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:52,120
Excuse me.
Hello.

297
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:54,120
What would you like to order?

298
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,000
The usual three.

299
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,039
Okay. One moment.

300
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:58,039
You think I believe that?

301
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,759
You coming to see me this late

302
00:13:59,759 --> 00:14:00,639
means something's up.

303
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,159
I'm happy.

304
00:14:02,159 --> 00:14:03,559
I missed you, alright?

305
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,720
Oh, please.

306
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,159
We were roommates

307
00:14:06,159 --> 00:14:06,919
for four years.

308
00:14:07,159 --> 00:14:08,159
I know you well.

309
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:09,279
Tell me the truth.

310
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:10,720
Are you thinking
about your old flame?

311
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,519
No, I'm not.

312
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,519
That's in the past.

313
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,559
In the past?

314
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,159
Then why

315
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:20,440
have you been single for five years?

316
00:14:20,679 --> 00:14:21,519
I just

317
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,120
haven't met the right person.

318
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:25,000
Fine, fine.

319
00:14:28,879 --> 00:14:29,399
Professor Lu.
Professor Lu.

320
00:14:29,919 --> 00:14:30,960
I'm late.

321
00:14:31,559 --> 00:14:32,720
No worries. We just got here.

322
00:14:32,919 --> 00:14:33,399
Have a seat.
Come on. Sit down.

323
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:36,519
Here.

324
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,080
Here's to us being together

325
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:39,840
again.
Cheers.

326
00:14:41,039 --> 00:14:41,720
Thank you, Professor Lu.

327
00:14:42,039 --> 00:14:42,759
Thank you, Professor Lu.

328
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:52,759
Here's your Aofei Group access card,

329
00:14:52,799 --> 00:14:54,360
meal card,

330
00:14:54,519 --> 00:14:55,200
and employee handbook.

331
00:14:55,919 --> 00:14:57,039
Starting tomorrow,

332
00:14:57,279 --> 00:14:58,000
you two

333
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:59,960
will be colleagues on the project team.

334
00:15:00,679 --> 00:15:01,440
Do a good job.

335
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,519
Professor Lu, thanks for the opportunity.

336
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:04,679
Oh,
Professor Lu,

337
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:06,879
I just went back home.

338
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,279
I brought you some local seafood.

339
00:15:08,399 --> 00:15:08,840
Alright.
I'll leave it here.

340
00:15:09,759 --> 00:15:10,759
I'll take it to your car later.

341
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:11,279
Okay.

342
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,440
Spit it out.

343
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:17,799
Why are you getting drunk?

344
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,799
Because I'm not happy.

345
00:15:21,399 --> 00:15:23,080
Because of your old flame?

346
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:28,120
I miss him.

347
00:15:28,759 --> 00:15:30,240
I miss him so much.

348
00:15:30,399 --> 00:15:31,960
I think about him every day.

349
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,240
It's been five years.

350
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,879
Doesn't he miss me at all?

351
00:15:36,639 --> 00:15:37,240
How can...

352
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,519
How can he just

353
00:15:39,519 --> 00:15:40,919
never contact me?

354
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:41,720
If you miss him,

355
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:42,759
go find him.

356
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:45,440
I have my pride.

357
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,639
I was the one who said we should

358
00:15:46,639 --> 00:15:47,600
stop contacting each other.

359
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:49,039
Why?

360
00:15:51,039 --> 00:15:52,759
I was trying to push him.

361
00:15:52,759 --> 00:15:54,000
I was afraid he'd give up.

362
00:15:54,399 --> 00:15:55,600
And he told me

363
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,080
to move forward and not look back,

364
00:15:57,279 --> 00:15:58,519
that he'd catch up himself.

365
00:15:58,759 --> 00:16:00,120
You actually believed that?

366
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,360
People change easily.

367
00:16:02,919 --> 00:16:03,840
To put it bluntly,

368
00:16:04,159 --> 00:16:05,519
he might have given up long ago.

369
00:16:06,039 --> 00:16:07,240
He might have even forgotten about you.

370
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,559
Maybe he really has forgotten about me.

371
00:16:12,159 --> 00:16:13,080
Do you

372
00:16:13,519 --> 00:16:14,639
still have his contact info?

373
00:16:15,559 --> 00:16:16,919
I do have his phone number.

374
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:18,639
Give me your phone.

375
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:20,440
What for?

376
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,559
Xing Wu, you

377
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:31,679
just got to Beijing.

378
00:16:31,799 --> 00:16:32,679
Did you find a place yet?

379
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:33,879
Found one.
It's right near here.

380
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:36,519
Professor,

381
00:16:36,519 --> 00:16:37,799
you know Xing Wu.

382
00:16:38,039 --> 00:16:38,639
He has to

383
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:39,840
have everything prepared in advance.

384
00:16:41,279 --> 00:16:41,840
What about you?

385
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,039
My sister's in Beijing.

386
00:16:43,399 --> 00:16:44,039
I'll stay with her.
Good.

387
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,120
You two,

388
00:16:46,639 --> 00:16:48,039
keep at it.

389
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,519
Make a life for yourselves in Beijing.

390
00:16:49,639 --> 00:16:50,039
Here.
For sure.

391
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:51,600
Okay.

392
00:16:53,039 --> 00:16:54,559
The call just didn't go through.

393
00:16:54,919 --> 00:16:55,600
Look at you.
You drank way too much.

394
00:16:56,639 --> 00:16:57,360
It's not a big deal.

395
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:59,519
Maybe he just didn't see it.

396
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:00,759
You...
Want me to take you home?

397
00:17:02,279 --> 00:17:02,720
No need.

398
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,279
My place is nearby.

399
00:17:04,279 --> 00:17:05,720
I'll take a walk and sober up.

400
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,319
Your ride's here.

401
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:08,920
Okay. You sure you're okay?

402
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:09,640
Yes.

403
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:11,279
Just text me when you get home.

404
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,079
I'm off then.
Bye.

405
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,079
Bye.

406
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:37,759
Okay. See you.
Okay.

407
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:39,160
Professor Lu, take care.

408
00:17:39,519 --> 00:17:40,079
- Okay.
- Take care.

409
00:17:50,799 --> 00:17:51,920
My ride will be here soon.

410
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,799
People change easily.

411
00:18:05,319 --> 00:18:06,160
To put it bluntly,

412
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:07,839
he might have given up long ago.

413
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:10,640
He might have even forgotten about you.

414
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:18,200
Xing Wu, did you really forget?

415
00:18:21,839 --> 00:18:22,960
Can we still spend

416
00:18:23,599 --> 00:18:24,960
next New Year's together?

417
00:18:27,079 --> 00:18:27,799
Where

418
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:29,799
do you plan to be next year?

419
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,160
That depends on how I do

420
00:18:33,519 --> 00:18:34,720
on my college entrance exam.

421
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,200
If possible,

422
00:18:38,119 --> 00:18:39,359
I'd like to come back here.

423
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:20,160
Hello?

424
00:19:21,119 --> 00:19:21,720
Where are you?

425
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:23,440
I texted you, but you didn't reply.

426
00:19:24,799 --> 00:19:25,880
I'm near my place.

427
00:19:27,119 --> 00:19:27,960
Are you drunk?

428
00:19:28,559 --> 00:19:29,359
No, I'm not.

429
00:20:13,279 --> 00:20:13,920
Qing Ye.

430
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,240
Why did you drink so much?

431
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,319
Let me take you home.

432
00:20:49,839 --> 00:20:50,880
Have some water.

433
00:20:52,039 --> 00:20:52,640
Xing Wu.

434
00:20:54,599 --> 00:20:55,240
Xing Wu.

435
00:20:57,519 --> 00:20:58,599
Is that you?

436
00:21:07,799 --> 00:21:08,599
It's Meng Ruihang.

437
00:21:26,519 --> 00:21:27,319
Get some rest.

438
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:28,359
I'm leaving.

439
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:28,279
How did I get home yesterday?

440
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:38,400
Hello?
Are you awake?

441
00:22:40,519 --> 00:22:41,720
Just woke up.

442
00:22:42,079 --> 00:22:42,880
Are you okay?

443
00:22:44,359 --> 00:22:45,279
Yeah, I guess.

444
00:22:45,839 --> 00:22:46,640
A little dizzy.

445
00:22:47,759 --> 00:22:49,480
You drank too much last night.

446
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:51,079
I couldn't stop you.

447
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:52,839
Let me tell you,

448
00:22:54,559 --> 00:22:55,720
starting today,

449
00:22:56,119 --> 00:22:57,359
I'm quitting drinking for three months.

450
00:22:57,759 --> 00:22:58,519
Hold me to it.

451
00:22:59,079 --> 00:22:59,799
it's not the drinking

452
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:01,240
you need to quit, but that person

453
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,759
you're waiting for who's not coming.

454
00:23:03,039 --> 00:23:04,519
When one door closes, another opens.

455
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,960
There's always a way forward.

456
00:23:06,759 --> 00:23:07,319
What,

457
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:09,240
you gonna introduce me to a hot guy?

458
00:23:09,519 --> 00:23:10,240
You guessed it.

459
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:11,920
Definitely good-looking

460
00:23:12,039 --> 00:23:12,759
and a good person.

461
00:23:12,960 --> 00:23:14,000
You're that sure?

462
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:15,359
Because it's my own brother.

463
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:16,519
He just got to Beijing.

464
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:17,759
I'm hooking you up with him for free.

465
00:23:18,039 --> 00:23:18,759
Don't mess around.
I can't handle that.

466
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,519
Besides, I'm not interested in that now.

467
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,359
Don't be formal with me.

468
00:23:23,759 --> 00:23:24,799
We're tight like that.

469
00:23:25,359 --> 00:23:26,319
Alright.

470
00:23:26,359 --> 00:23:27,559
Matchmaking time is over.

471
00:23:27,680 --> 00:23:28,440
I'm going to work.

472
00:23:28,759 --> 00:23:29,720
I have

473
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:30,880
a project summary meeting today.

474
00:23:32,039 --> 00:23:32,839
I gotta go. Bye.

475
00:23:48,519 --> 00:23:49,359
Think about what I said
this morning.

476
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:51,680
You're serious?
Of course.

477
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:53,759
Let me give you
a quick rundown.

478
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:55,279
Just hear me out.

479
00:23:55,599 --> 00:23:56,519
I'm not interested.

480
00:23:56,559 --> 00:23:57,680
My brother, Qu Xing.

481
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:58,880
Graduated from Northwestern Polytechnical University.

482
00:23:59,119 --> 00:24:00,200
He's in grad school now.

483
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:02,079
He just got to Beijing a few days ago.

484
00:24:02,359 --> 00:24:03,680
He's working on a project

485
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:05,119
at Aofei Group with his advisor.

486
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,359
Great.

487
00:24:07,759 --> 00:24:08,599
Young and talented.
What do you think?

488
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:10,720
No.

489
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:13,119
It's okay if you're not into my brother.

490
00:24:13,559 --> 00:24:14,839
If you want,

491
00:24:15,039 --> 00:24:16,279
he also has a colleague

492
00:24:16,359 --> 00:24:17,160
who just got to Beijing too.

493
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:18,839
Let's grab dinner tonight.

494
00:24:19,319 --> 00:24:20,200
I owe him
a welcome dinner anyway.

495
00:24:22,279 --> 00:24:23,359
Wait, why are you

496
00:24:23,799 --> 00:24:24,680
suddenly so eager

497
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:25,799
to set me up?

498
00:24:26,359 --> 00:24:28,119
I just hate seeing you like this.

499
00:24:28,839 --> 00:24:29,599
They say

500
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:31,240
you need to move on to get over someone.

501
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,440
Actually,

502
00:24:32,599 --> 00:24:33,559
you only really move on

503
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,559
when someone new comes along.

504
00:24:36,319 --> 00:24:36,880
Alright.

505
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:38,200
Send me the time and place.

506
00:24:38,839 --> 00:24:39,400
So

507
00:24:40,079 --> 00:24:40,640
you're saying yes?

508
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:42,920
You're buying anyway.

509
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,319
I might as well come for the free meal.

510
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:45,000
Qing Ye.

511
00:24:45,519 --> 00:24:46,119
Ms. Zhu, hello.

512
00:24:46,759 --> 00:24:47,279
Ms. Zhu.
Qing Ye.

513
00:24:48,279 --> 00:24:49,039
Congratulations.

514
00:24:49,319 --> 00:24:50,319
Your project cleared the kickoff meeting.

515
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:51,519
That fast?

516
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:54,000
The board is very bullish

517
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:54,519
on the project

518
00:24:54,599 --> 00:24:56,119
and says they'll go in big on it.

519
00:24:56,559 --> 00:24:58,240
Looks like what you dug up on that beach

520
00:24:58,240 --> 00:24:59,920
wasn't sand, but gold.

521
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,039
Then I need to hurry up

522
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,839
and go to Chang Island for a follow-up trip.

523
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:03,720
Okay. Good luck.

524
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:11,519
Mr. Xing, you're still busy?

525
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:17,680
Xing,

526
00:25:18,359 --> 00:25:19,839
take a break. Perk up.

527
00:25:22,599 --> 00:25:23,799
I'm good. You have it.

528
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:26,720
You really work hard.

529
00:25:27,759 --> 00:25:28,960
I just sent Professor Lu the design

530
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:30,680
I stayed up several nights working on,

531
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,000
and he sent me to help you.

532
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:33,640
Don't even mention it.

533
00:25:34,319 --> 00:25:35,359
The dataset is too big.

534
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:36,680
I went to the bathroom for a second

535
00:25:36,799 --> 00:25:37,720
and the processor crashed.

536
00:25:38,039 --> 00:25:38,519
My sister

537
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:39,920
is buying dinner tonight.
I'll bring you along.

538
00:25:41,039 --> 00:25:41,920
Consider it my apology.

539
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:42,920
Okay?

540
00:25:43,519 --> 00:25:44,039
I'm not going.

541
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:45,880
Hey,

542
00:25:46,039 --> 00:25:47,680
my sister specifically told me

543
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:48,599
to bring the best guy

544
00:25:48,599 --> 00:25:49,839
I know

545
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:50,920
to introduce to her friend.

546
00:25:51,039 --> 00:25:51,920
Don't say no.

547
00:25:52,519 --> 00:25:53,359
Thanks,

548
00:25:54,519 --> 00:25:55,200
but no thanks.

549
00:25:55,759 --> 00:25:56,720
I know.

550
00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:57,920
You still have that one person
you're hung up on.

551
00:25:59,039 --> 00:26:00,160
Just do me a favor.

552
00:26:00,559 --> 00:26:01,720
If it really turns into a blind date,

553
00:26:01,799 --> 00:26:03,160
you gotta have my back.

554
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:05,839
Look.

555
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:07,519
This is my sister, Qu Bing.

556
00:26:07,599 --> 00:26:09,039
And this is her college roommate.

557
00:26:09,279 --> 00:26:10,759
A genius who graduated from Qingbei.

558
00:26:11,039 --> 00:26:11,920
Up-and-comer in the industry.

559
00:26:12,319 --> 00:26:12,920
Pretty, right?

560
00:26:16,759 --> 00:26:17,319
Fine, don't go then.
Wait.

561
00:26:21,039 --> 00:26:21,519
I'll go.
What time?

562
00:26:25,839 --> 00:26:26,440
Interested in her?

563
00:26:28,079 --> 00:26:28,880
Free meal.

564
00:26:29,559 --> 00:26:30,359
Why not?

565
00:26:33,119 --> 00:26:33,799
It's a deal then.

566
00:26:50,359 --> 00:26:50,839
This table.

567
00:27:00,279 --> 00:27:01,400
Sir, here's the menu.

568
00:27:01,519 --> 00:27:02,160
What would you like to order?
Take a look first.

569
00:27:03,079 --> 00:27:03,519
Okay.

570
00:27:08,039 --> 00:27:08,680
Xing Wu,

571
00:27:09,519 --> 00:27:11,160
you look so good in that outfit.

572
00:27:11,599 --> 00:27:12,799
You're stealing my thunder.

573
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,160
Really?

574
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:15,519
Totally.

575
00:27:16,519 --> 00:27:17,640
You're not trying to

576
00:27:17,720 --> 00:27:18,920
become my brother-in-law, are you?

577
00:27:20,279 --> 00:27:21,240
You're overthinking it.

578
00:27:23,079 --> 00:27:23,519
I'm telling you,

579
00:27:23,519 --> 00:27:24,720
the restaurant I picked

580
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:25,519
is definitely solid.

581
00:27:25,799 --> 00:27:27,519
They have great sea urchin egg custard

582
00:27:27,599 --> 00:27:28,160
